@mjsax should I completely remove https://github.com/simplesteph/kafka/blob/0c7c204fc0eb67b9f797e685eafca34ab99134d5/clients/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/producer/ProducerRecord.java#L60 ?

Basically any API that hardcodes `partition`. My biggest concern is that the doc states everywhere that if a user sends a key, then the message will always go to the same partition. This API allows people to break that guarantee quite easily? 

This will guide how I'll write my KIP
